{"tid":348434,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】我IG俾啲奇怪人HACK左，唔知咩語言黎","createTime":"2017-08-05T16:38:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-06T13:10:43.000Z","uid":48498,"like":10,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1cc84fa61edd77f8872f580486c122154b93fbe2","tid":348434,"uid":48498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T16:38:26.000Z","msg":"是咁的，除左自己IG Account,小弟N年前開左間ig shop仔賣下啲魔術，玩具同啤牌咁（純粹係外國訂啲自己想玩嘅野，訂多幾件慳番運費咁）<br />\n每次想買野先update下，都有2000幾 followers咁。<br />\n<br />\n今日再上嘅時候，佢話我個Account係第二個國家俾人突入左，之後輸入番就已經話冇依個Ac,,變左下圖依個<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/x8hyvgd5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fx8hyvgd5&h=ae89d966&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/wu1k3qj8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fwu1k3qj8&h=38bcbd2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一開始諗，咁可能係我記錯帳戶喇，但係望清楚佢啲followers數字同我一樣，再禁入去全部都係我啲舊客同朋友黎，之後連我正身Ac都有follow<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再用Google Search番我舊Ig shop個名，條link都係番去依個ac....<br />\n<br />\n依家有幾個問題問全能嘅連登仔：<br />\n<br />\n1.究竟係咩文黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢hack黎有咩用<br />\n同埋係講緊咩<br />\n2.我除左 report可以做啲咩？<br />\n3.我傳啲咩msg俾佢好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"001c9e5dc5cad60b78ca9353635499ba59eff11f","tid":348434,"uid":48498,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T16:39:43.000Z","msg":"佢仲要用咩啲火燒 蒙羅麗莎頭像<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f47abda947e52f6c0119b955398351836850445e","tid":348434,"uid":48498,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T16:40:36.000Z","msg":"下面黑色背景嗰啲圖案又係咩黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪要下世小心啲<img src=\"/assets/